Drowned 31th of August Lat 2b 5b Long 51 22' and having been washed overboard
Dec. 4th sent to the hospital at Colombo. Complaints about pain in the head with fits. Dec. 8th Discharged not having showed any symtom. Dec. 10th off duty. Dec. 11th Discharged at Colombo.
